&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help to drive interest and opportunities for the Arkestro Sales Team through outbound activities such as cold calling, emails and LinkedIn&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pitch our company to potential customers and qualify leads before passing off to Account Executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in marketing campaigns to drive attendance and interest for internal events such as Optimal, webinars, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively seek new business opportunities in the market through multiple tools such as Zoominfo&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share qualitative and quantitative feedback with Business Development and Sales Leaders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously update our CRM to make sure all accounts are up-to-date&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
